description: This is a follow-up to a request, I'm back so I'll fulfil most, so go ahead and describe the pic you want or send an imgur link in the comments. Credits to >Project Sekai: Colorful Stage<for the pic. This code was created by me, do give feedback for improvements in the comments. If you want more fixed roblox styles just click BoopBop at the top, or you can click DittoDino below for some mediocre youtube progressbars.
